des: The Force Five Podcast is all about talking movies…with one small twist: I force my weekly guest to come up with a movie themed 'five list' (i.e. 5 incredible movie scores, 5 great movie posters, top 5 car chases, 5 movies that remind you of summer) beforehand - and then we discuss our picks on-air.
